ygData.messageBody:
I didn't. I spent 30 minutes at 5:30pm Pacific trying to log into Veeshan

At 6:03pm Pacific on Veeshan I did /movelog yes
at 6:04pm Pacific on Veeshan I bid all my friends goodbye who were on
at 6:35pm Pacific on Veeshan I camped out
at 6:40pm Pacific I logged into Tallon Zek and played my dark elf
Shadowknight for several hours.

I don't want to get any more xp on Veeshan since I may lose a bunch of it
when they move the backup files to a new server.

Lyrnia Jongleur
Traveller of Norrath - Saryn
